record.field: A stockable product is a product for which you manage stock. The "Inventory" app has to be installed. A consumable product, on the other hand, is a product for which stock is not managed. A service is a non-material product you provide. A digital content is a non-material product you sell online. The files attached to the products are the one that are sold on the e-commerce such as e-books, music, pictures,... The "Digital Product" module has to be installed.
